1) add reunion.xml to your $FGDATA/Materials/regions/
2) add the following line to your $FGDATA/Materials/regions/materials.xml:
	
	<region include="Materials/regions/reunion.xml"/>

	after 
	
	<!-- Africa -->
	<region include="Materials/regions/africa_savanna.xml"/>
